snippet.title: iCkEdMeL
snippet.description:
iCkEdMeL - The obscurity of what's happening to children in our society. From parents, CPS, DCFS, the missing and the systems in place that are supposed to protect them. On my platform, we ask questions and bring awareness.

I've been featured on KHOU, FOX, ABC, Inside Edition, BET, MSN, and TheGrio.
I cover the latest news until I come across a story that really touches people. 
From there we dig until every detail has surfaced.

Mailing Address:

Hollywood, FL 33021
